data.description: Great location in Greenwood Arkansas! Close to shopping, schools, church, etc. Beautiful Bell Park is close by for all kinds of outdoor activities. This roomy 4 bedroom home features vaulted ceiling in the living area with beautiful wood beams and woodburning brick fireplace (currently has electric insert). 3 full baths will surely make things easier for your group. Kitchen has new painted cabinets, stainless appliances and a breakfast area right by the window. Formal dining room or office space off to the right of the kitchen. Covered back deck overlooks huge fenced yard. HVAC approx 5 years old, Roof approx 7 years old. Seller is offering $5000 at closing for any buyer needed expenses with acceptable offer. This home also qualifies for no money down with buyer approval of USDA RD loan.
